@startuml 时序图-获取AI解梦
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title 时序图：获取AI解梦

actor 用户 as User
participant "InterpretationController" as Controller
participant "DreamInterpretationService" as Service
participant "KeywordExtractor" as Extractor
participant "DreamInterpretation" as Interpretation
database "数据库" as DB

User -> Controller: 选择梦境，点击「AI解梦」
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: interpret(dreamId)
activate Service

Service -> DB: 查询梦境内容
DB --> Service: Dream

Service -> Extractor: extractKeywords(dreamContent)
activate Extractor
Extractor --> Service: List<String> 关键词
deactivate Extractor

Service -> Service: 根据关键词匹配解梦规则

alt 已有解梦结果
  Service -> DB: 查询历史解梦
  DB --> Service: DreamInterpretation
  Service --> Controller: DreamInterpretation
else 需要生成新解梦
  Service -> Interpretation: 生成解梦内容
  activate Interpretation
  Interpretation --> Service: DreamInterpretation
  deactivate Interpretation
  Service -> DB: 保存解梦结果
  DB --> Service: 成功
  Service --> Controller: DreamInterpretation
end

deactivate Service

Controller --> User: 展示解梦结果
deactivate Controller

User -> Controller: 点击「收藏解梦」（可选）
Controller -> DB: 保存收藏记录
Controller --> User: 收藏成功

@enduml
